how do I add our tax number to the account?

To add your tax number to your NewsBreak ad account, you can follow the steps outlined in our Account Management Guide. Here's the link to the guide: [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide). If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
i can't find the right place to submit the tax number

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble finding where to submit your tax number. Please make sure you are logged into your Ad Manager account. If you still can't find the right place, I recommend reaching out to our support team for further assistance. You can email them at adsupport@newsbreak.com with your issue, and they will be able to guide you through the process.
